  "description": [
    "War Rages Right Here PROBLEM OF PEACE MUST NOT BE OVERSIMPLIFIED By GEORGE EMMERSON Hysham Lowndes Maurys article on the war in Korea in the July 21 issue of the Voice is to be generous a dangerous oversimplification of a great and per plexing problem the problem of World Peace of which the situation in Korea is merely a fragment which the US is not the only nation concerned and one that has so far baf fled and vexed thinking people the world over The UN organization of fers the only hopeit must not fail and it has acted in Korea A study of the voting on this issue shows aston ishing unanimity among the member nations even India voted in favor The legal position is abundantly clear The Northern Koreans have invad ed South Korea with a well prepared equipped and organized army despite their awareness of the position of the United Nations on this matter and the possibility of endangering the peace and lives of the common people the world over Whatever the excuses for this belligerent action the North Kor eans have taken the law into their own hands and put themselves in the posi tion of"
